#14322
Hidden Grove~
There is a small wooden house built here, surrounded by large trees.  All
along the ground there is exercise gear.  Oddly, there is also enough
weapons here to support a small militia, and along the walls there are
practice dummies and several bails or hay which have been beaten into little
piles of grain.  This must be some sort of hidden war prep area.  
~
