#14323
Dock~
This massive oak dock hovers on planks over the waters of the lake. 
There are several little bird nests that sit in the trees around the area,
and it seems like some other small animals make their homes in this area. 
To the west there is a large row of trees and to the south-east is the
Aegis.  Across the lake there is a large building.  
~
