#14324
Lakeside~
The bank of the lake stands to the north.  Little ripples of water seem
to wash up on the bank of ginger colored sands lining the clear waters.  The
smell of rainfall and honey are in the air, caused by the lovely serenity
and clarity of the lake.  To the south stands the Aegis Inn, and woods
continue onward to the west.  
~
