#14325
Lawn before Aegis~
The shiny green grass before the massive Inn to the north seems to emit a
subtle, easy going aura to it.  Northbound, the Aegis Inn stands with two
stacked stories of well constructed oak.  The Inn itself has a easy woodsy
look to it from the outside, and the windows looking inside seem to be made
of crystaline pressed glass which gives it a slight reflective property to
it.  The subtle sounds of a lake are heard to the far north.  
~
