#14327
Back Room~
On the wall next to the door there is a sign that reads 'Employee Area'
on it.  The back room room is rather large with a series of interconnected
cart shelves all around, all holding some sort of food product or beverage. 
The walls are clean white, unlike the rest of the Inn, and the counters are
well organized next to the stoves and ovens.  To the north a door leads
outside and to the common area lies directly south.  
~
