#14328
Aegis Inn, Second Floor~
The hallways lead off into several directions where guest Inn rooms are
available for rent to the many patrons of the city.  The walls are lined
with paintings of heroes from the ages, and there are small tables in the
hall which hold on them exotic flower blossoms in cast marble planters.  An
access stairway upward leads to the roof, and below there is the common area
of the Inn.  
~
