Basement~
In this basement, in a small section to the north, there is a set of
four water heater tanks and all of the electrical panel to run the Inn.  To
the south of the spacious basement, there is a place where row after row of
liquer and wine bottles are lin in a near retentive manner on the cast iron
racks.  The pipes lining the ceiling are also piping hot to be under.  
